# Profit Or Loss Insurance After Tax Amount

## identifier
de8546

## type
float

## definition
This is the profit (loss) after tax or the relevant period. This item is calculated in accordance with the relevant Prudential Standards and represents profit (loss) after tax of both continuing and discontinued operations.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=ProfitOrLoss.Insurance.AfterTax.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr3.02.05
- period=duration
